merican college football season}}\n{{NCAATeamSeason\n| mode = football\n| year = 2018\n| team=Butler Bulldogs\n| image=Butler Bulldogs wordmark.svg\n| image_size= 250\n| conference= Pioneer Football League\n| division= \n| short_conf= PFL\n| STATSRank = \n| FCSCoachRank = \n| record = 4\u20137\n| conf_record = 2\u20136\n| head_coach= [[Jeff Voris]]\n| hc_year = 13th\n| off_coach=Kyle Conner\n| oc_year =\n| def_coach=Joe Cheshire\n| dc_year = \n| off_scheme= \n| def_scheme=\n| stadium= [[Bud and Jackie Sellick Bowl]]<br>(Capacity: 5,647)\n| champion = \n| bowl = \n| bowl_result =\n}}\n{{2018 Pioneer Football League standings}}\nThe '''2018 Butler Bulldogs football team''' represented [[Butler University]] in the [[2018 NCAA Division I FCS football season]]. They were led by 13th-year head coach [[Jeff Voris]] and played their home games at the [[Bud and Jackie Sellick Bowl]]. They were members of the [[Pioneer Football League]]. They finished the season 4\u20137, 2\u20136 in PFL play to finish in a three-way tie for seventh place.\n\n==Previous season==\nThe Bulldogs finished the [[2017 Butler Bulldogs football team|2017 season]] 6\u20135, 4\u20134 in PFL play to finish in a tie for sixth place.\n\n==Preseason==\n===Preseason All-PFL team===\nThe PFL released their preseason all-PFL team on July 30, 2018, with the Bulldogs having four players selected.<ref>http://www.pioneer-football.org/news/archives/2018/1361/twelve-first-team-all-pfl-returnees-highlight-preseason-all-pfl-team/</ref>\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n'''Offense'''\n\nPace Temple \u2013 WR\n\nBobby Jensen \u2013 OL\n\nDakota Sneed \u2013 OL\n\n'''Special teams'''\n\nDrew Bevalhimer \u2013 K\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Preseason coaches poll===\nThe PFL released their preseason coaches poll on July 31, 2018, with the Bulldogs predicted to finish in a tie for fourth place.<ref>http://www.pioneer-football.org/news/archives/2018/1362/defending-champion-san-diego-edges-dayton-in-pfl-preseason-coaches-poll/</ref>\n